{"id":70,"parent_id":52,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":70,"title":"Exodus 18","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ex.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 18"],[".studySummary",["i","Jethro comes to Moses bringing Moses’ wife and sons and offers sacrifices to the Lord—Moses sits in the judgment seat and hears all cases—Jethro counsels Moses to teach the law, to appoint lesser judges, and to delegate power to them."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1","order":"02.03.018.6323"},["b","1"],"When",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Jethro"],", the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"priest"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"Midian"],", Moses’ father in law, heard of all that",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"God"],"had done for Moses, and for Israel his people,",["i","and"],"that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had brought Israel out of Egypt;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.2","order":"02.03.018.6324"},["b","2"],"Then Jethro, Moses’ father in law, took",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Zipporah"],", Moses’ wife, after he had sent her back,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.3","order":"02.03.018.6325"},["b","3"],"And her two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sons"],"; of which the name of the one",["i","was"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Gershom"],"; for he said,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"I"],"have been an alien in a strange land:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.4","order":"02.03.018.6326"},["b","4"],"And the name of the other",["i","was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Eliezer"],"; for the God of my father,",["i","said he, was"],"mine help, and delivered me from the sword of Pharaoh:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.5","order":"02.03.018.6327"},["b","5"],"And Jethro, Moses’ father in law, came with his sons and his wife unto Moses into the wilderness, where he encamped at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"mount of God"],":"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.6","order":"02.03.018.6328"},["b","6"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"said"],"unto Moses, I thy father in law Jethro am come unto thee, and thy wife, and her two sons with her."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.7","order":"02.03.018.6329"},["b","7"],"¶And Moses went out to meet his father in law, and did obeisance, and kissed him; and they asked each other of",["i","their"],"welfare; and they came into the tent."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.8","order":"02.03.018.6330"},["b","8"],"And Moses told his father in law all that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had done unto Pharaoh and to the Egyptians for Israel’s sake,",["i","and"],"all the travail that had come upon them by the way, and",["i","how"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"delivered them."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.9","order":"02.03.018.6331"},["b","9"],"And Jethro rejoiced for all the goodness which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had done to Israel, whom he had delivered out of the hand of the Egyptians."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.10","order":"02.03.018.6332"},["b","10"],"And Jethro said, Blessed",["i","be"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", who hath delivered you out of the hand of the Egyptians, and out of the hand of Pharaoh, who hath delivered the people from under the hand of the Egyptians."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.11","order":"02.03.018.6333"},["b","11"],"Now I know that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"greater than all gods: for in the thing wherein they dealt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"proudly"],["i","he was"],"above them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.12","order":"02.03.018.6334"},["b","12"],"And Jethro, Moses’ father in law, took a burnt offering and sacrifices for God: and Aaron came, and all the elders of Israel, to eat",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"bread"],"with Moses’ father in law before God."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.13","order":"02.03.018.6335"},["b","13"],"¶And it came to pass on the morrow, that Moses sat to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"judge"],"the people: and the people stood by Moses from the morning unto the evening."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.14","order":"02.03.018.6336"},["b","14"],"And when Moses’ father in law saw all that he did to the people, he said, What",["i","is"],"this thing that thou doest to the people? why sittest thou thyself alone, and all the people stand by thee from morning unto even?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.15","order":"02.03.018.6337"},["b","15"],"And Moses said unto his father in law, Because the people come unto me to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"inquire"],"of God:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.16","order":"02.03.018.6338"},["b","16"],"When they have a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"matter"],", they come unto me; and I judge between one and another, and I do make",["i","them"],"know the statutes of God, and his laws."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.17","order":"02.03.018.6339"},["b","17"],"And Moses’ father in law said unto him, The thing that thou doest",["i","is"],"not good."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.18","order":"02.03.018.6340"},["b","18"],"Thou wilt surely wear away, both thou, and this people that",["i","is"],"with thee: for this thing",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"too"],"heavy for thee; thou art not able to perform it thyself alone."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.19","order":"02.03.018.6341"},["b","19"],"Hearken now unto my voice, I will give thee counsel, and God shall be with thee:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Be"],"thou for the people to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"God-ward"],", that thou mayest bring the causes unto God:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20","order":"02.03.018.6342"},["b","20"],"And thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"teach"],"them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"ordinances"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"laws"],", and shalt shew them the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"way"],"wherein they must",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_20e"},"walk"],", and the work that they must do."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21","order":"02.03.018.6343"},["b","21"],"Moreover thou shalt provide out of all the people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"able"],"men, such as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"fear"],"God,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"men of truth"],", hating",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_21d"},"covetousness"],"; and place",["i","such"],"over them,",["i","to be"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_21e"},"rulers"],"of thousands,",["i","and"],"rulers of",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_21f"},"hundreds"],", rulers of fifties, and rulers of tens:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.22","order":"02.03.018.6344"},["b","22"],"And let them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"judge"],"the people at all seasons: and it shall be,",["i","that"],"every great matter they shall bring unto thee, but every small matter they shall judge: so shall it be easier for thyself, and they shall bear",["i","the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"burden"]],"with thee."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.23","order":"02.03.018.6345"},["b","23"],"If thou shalt do this thing, and God command thee",["i","so,"],"then thou shalt be able to endure, and all this people shall also go to their place in peace."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.24","order":"02.03.018.6346"},["b","24"],"So Moses hearkened to the voice of his father in law, and did all that he had said."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.25","order":"02.03.018.6347"},["b","25"],"And Moses chose able men out of all Israel, and made them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"heads"],"over the people, rulers of thousands, rulers of hundreds, rulers of fifties, and rulers of tens."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.26","order":"02.03.018.6348"},["b","26"],"And they judged the people at all seasons: the hard causes they brought unto Moses, but every small matter they judged themselves."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.27","order":"02.03.018.6349"},["b","27"],"¶And Moses let his father in law depart; and he went his way into his own land."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1a","order":"02.03.018.6350"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-melchizedek"},"TG Priesthood, Melchizedek"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1b","order":"02.03.018.6352"},["b","1b"],["span.small","JST"],"Ex. 18:1 …",["i","high priest"],"…",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.6.6-16"},"D&C 84:6 (6–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1c","order":"02.03.018.6354"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/25.2.1-6"},"Gen. 25:2 (1–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/2.16.15-16"},"Ex. 2:16 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1d","order":"02.03.018.6356"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.8"},"Ps. 106:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.2a","order":"02.03.018.6358"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/2.21"},"Ex. 2:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.3a","order":"02.03.018.6360"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.29"},"Acts 7:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.3b","order":"02.03.018.6362"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/2.22.21-22"},"Ex. 2:22 (21–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/23.15"},"1 Chr. 23:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.3c","order":"02.03.018.6364"},["b","3c"],["span.small","HEB"],"I have been a sojourner in a foreign land."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.4a","order":"02.03.018.6366"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"God of help."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.5a","order":"02.03.018.6368"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.1"},"Ex. 3:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.27"},"4:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.6a","order":"02.03.018.6370"},["b","6a"],["span.small","IE"],"sent word."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.11a","order":"02.03.018.6372"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.51.46-55"},"Luke 1:51 (46–55)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.12a","order":"02.03.018.6374"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/14.18"},"Gen. 14:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.13a","order":"02.03.018.6376"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/7.25"},"Ezra 7:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/29.11.11-44"},"Mosiah 29:11 (11–44)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.4"},"Alma 46:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.74.74,78"},"D&C 107:74 (74, 78)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.15a","order":"02.03.018.6378"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.7"},"Amos 3:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/28.6"},"Mosiah 28:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/27.10.7,10"},"Alma 27:10 (7, 10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.23"},"43:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/102.23"},"D&C 102:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.18"},"JS—H 1:18"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"TG Priesthood, Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.16a","order":"02.03.018.6380"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.1.1-8"},"1 Cor. 6:1 (1–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.18a","order":"02.03.018.6382"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.14.14-17"},"Num. 11:14 (14–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/1.9"},"Deut. 1:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.4"},"D&C 10:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.19a","order":"02.03.018.6384"},["b","19a"],["span.small","OR"],"You represent the people before God."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.19b","order":"02.03.018.6386"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.16"},"Ex. 4:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20a","order":"02.03.018.6388"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/7.25"},"Ezra 7:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.81"},"D&C 88:81"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teacher"},"TG Teacher"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20b","order":"02.03.018.6390"},["b","20b"],["span.small","OR"],"laws and doctrine.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20c","order":"02.03.018.6392"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"20d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20d","order":"02.03.018.6394"},["b","20d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.6"},"John 14:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"20e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.20e","order":"02.03.018.6396"},["b","20e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21a","order":"02.03.018.6398"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/1.15.12-18"},"Deut. 1:15 (12–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/19.5.5-10"},"2 Chr. 19:5 (5–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21b","order":"02.03.018.6400"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/23.3"},"2 Sam. 23:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/19.9.7-9"},"2 Chr. 19:9 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/7.2"},"Neh. 7:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/29.13"},"Mosiah 29:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reverence"},"TG Reverence"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21c","order":"02.03.018.6402"},["b","21c"],["span.small","OR"],"faithful or trustworthy men."],["div",{"id":"21d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21d","order":"02.03.018.6404"},["b","21d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/16.19"},"Deut. 16:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/8.3.1-4"},"1 Sam. 8:3 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/19.7.5-10"},"2 Chr. 19:7 (5–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21e","order":"02.03.018.6406"},["b","21e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"21f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21f","order":"02.03.018.6408"},["b","21f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.3.2-3"},"D&C 136:3 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.22a","order":"02.03.018.6410"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"TG Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.22b","order":"02.03.018.6412"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"TG Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.25a","order":"02.03.018.6414"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],"."]]}
